title: Neapolitan Crèche Foldout
description:
Elaborate, complex, and wondrous, the Neapolitan crèche is a rare example of the genre and a once-in-a-lifetime acquisition for the Art Institute. Bring the Creche home with this 6-panel accordion that includes a die-cut ornament.

Accordion measures: folded 3.75 in. X 12.25 in. ; flat 21.25 in. X 12.25 in.
